"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144734","Ministry of Justice","false","2019-09-09","<p>I refer the honourable member to my response of 3 September to Question 282465.</p>","Charnwood","Edward Argar","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144734/answer",,,,,,"2019-09-09T15:46:43.777Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144734/answer","Biography information for Edward Argar","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144734/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2019-09-04","Dangerous Driving: Sentencing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, whether he plans to (a) create an offence of causing serious injury by careless driving and (b) increase the maximum penalties for causing death by dangerous driving.","false","Biography information for Stephanie Peacock","Barnsley East","Stephanie Peacock","286821"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144735","Scotland Office","false","2019-09-09","<p>My officials continue to engage with the Islands partners and most recently met with the Islands Deal Programme Director on 2 August and 4 September to discuss next steps.</p><p> </p><p>Officials also spoke with the Leader of Orkney Islands Council on 27 August.</p><p> </p><p>We expect to receive the latest suite of proposals from the Islands partners later this month.</p>","Dumfries and Galloway","Mr Alister Jack","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144735/answer",,,,,,"2019-09-09T16:41:38.977Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144735/answer","Biography information for Mr Alister Jack","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1144735/answer",,,,,"2","Scotland","Scotland","2019-09-04","City Region Deals and Local Growth Deals: Scotland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Scotland, with reference to the Prime Minister’s announcement of 28 July 2019 on City Region and Growth deals, what information has been made available to(a) Comhairle nan Eilean Siar, (b) Orkney Islands Council and (c) Shetland Islands Council on a deal for the Islands.","false","Biography information for Angus Brendan MacNeil","Na h-Eileanan an Iar","Angus Brendan MacNeil","286687"
