at plans they have to instruct the Clinical Commissioning Groups in South East London to publish the evidence it relied on in developing its policy of not providing fertility treatment to single women.","false","Biography information for Lord Hunt of Kings Heath",,"Lord Hunt of Kings Heath","HL17718"
